I  have  resolved it.
In my project with express, I used middleware named [connect-livereload](https://github.com/intesso/connect-livereload) which affected the zip packet transmission.

add ignore option which contain '.zip'

```
 app.use(require('connect-livereload')({
    port: 6000,
    ignore: [ '.zip']
  }));
```
